      "id": "0ee05874-1142-4f9a-8860-c037b20c0097",
      "front": "What is the formula for Scaled Dot-Product Attention?",
      "back": "$\\text{Attention}(Q, K, V) = \\text{softmax}\\left(\\frac{QK^T}{\\sqrt{d_k}}\\right)V$",
      "anchor_object": "95c69c42-11f7-5bdf-b5d8-77e3d72397b1",
