      "id": "209b6356-4f04-4f25-ad13-57471b5c9e78",
      "front": "Why is the dot-product of the query and key scaled by $1/\\sqrt{d_k}$?",
      "back": "To counteract the effects of large dot products in high dimensions, which push the softmax into regions of extremely small gradients.",
